        <title type="html"><![CDATA[P2【3.产品调研进阶】]]></title>
        <id>https://www.meiyan.in/post/p23chan-pin-diao-yan-jin-jie/</id>
        <link href="https://www.meiyan.in/post/p23chan-pin-diao-yan-jin-jie/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-11-29T08:06:15.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>##3.1抄也是一门学问<br>
<strong>产品分析和竞品调研</strong><br>
<strong>3.1.1产品分析与竞品调研的概念</strong><br>
<strong>为什么要做产品分析与调研？</strong><br>
产品分析：了解产品概况，具体功能模块的产品功能设计与逻辑<br>
竞品调研：竞品检测，分析竞品情况<br>
日常交流学习，提升产品感觉<br>
<strong>产品调研常见误区</strong><br>
产品调研报告  不等于  行业分析报告<br>
产品调研报告  不等于  产品体验报告<br>
产品调研  不等于 写产品报告 （重点是调研过程）<br>
不要用“看起来很高深的数据”的分析过程来证明自己的结论是靠谱的<br>
不用期望通过竞品调研来证明自己的存在感（多看竞品优秀的地方）</p>
<p>不做产品调研的PM是不合格的，优秀的PM一定能做好产品调研</p>
<p><strong>3.1.2产品分析与调研的方法</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606638811926.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.1明确调研的背景与目的</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606639880256.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606639553912.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.2选定目标产品</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606639803405.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.3深度体验产品</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640036322.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.4还原产品</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640118198.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.5分析产品</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640252900.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.6产品迭代与运营分析</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640504378.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640602636.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.7横向比较同类型的产品</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640750169.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.8撰写调研分析报告</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1606640927418.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>2.9推广报告</strong><br>
内部分享：在公司内部建立分享会<br>
外部发布：在第三方平台表达出来</p>
<p>##3.2产品初期针对行业的调研<br>
<strong>关于PMF的概念</strong><br>
产品脱离市场：足记<br>
产品被市场套牢：诺基亚、柯达<br>
<strong>3.2.1产业地图-产业链梳理与市场盘点</strong><br>
产业地图包括三个方面：1.市场趋势和规模 2.产业链梳理：业务抽象化表达 3.主要玩家和商业模式<br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608809043051.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608809313693.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608809428249.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608809491511.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608809743134.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<strong>3.2.2典型产品的结构化分析</strong><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608809948458.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608810075923.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608810188379.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
核心业务结构：生产者-消费者之间的业务关系<br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608810259942.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608810372714.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://www.meiyan.in//post-images/1608810961632.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
